{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 443.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on this train-- the next-- the train that was next to us, there was-- they just piled all the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was literally full with dead skeletons, because that's what they were was skeletons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes, we would-- I think we-- we survived because, sometimes, they would-- we would go-- they let us go for water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was able to beg for food on the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- German-- I would knock on German houses, and things like that, because I think I had to share whatever I got with the guards.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes, the military, German military trains, would pass by close enough where we could see them, and stop them, and-- and beg them for something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And sometimes, I would get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the first-- but was-- was such starvation that we-- we ate grass.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I took grass, and we were able to have little fires and-- and boil the grass.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was-- all it was, it was just green water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think some people probably ate flesh, human flesh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I think so, with-- people were whispering, you know, they're eating flesh.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had-- we were living-- like the young people were like in packs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I was part of a pack that, maybe, had 10, 12 members.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever food we're able to get, we would share it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would cook it, and each one had the right to taste it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a taste.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't think we had many casualties among the young people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you-- you know, you have to remember, we were in much better physical condition than the rest of the population.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
